Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:05.44,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Dear Onee-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:11.61,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, I failed to get the spinach that was on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.70,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Am I really qualified to be your younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:22.39,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,You must hate your little sister who fails repeatedl{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:28.04,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I tr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, it’s never enough to make you notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.30,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Yamada Kyou,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.33,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Yamada Asu, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom went to heaven the year Asu was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, we were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room,\Ndilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? It’s already this late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up! We’re going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just three more minutes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is really dark, even in the morning.{T-3,2,1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All because that high-rise got built next doo{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.{TIME WARP TO A YEAR IN THE FUTURE (either that or the japanese are some of the damn fastest construction workers in the universe).}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weather’s great toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.{LOL THEY LIVE IN THE LUXURY MANSION COMPLEX}{wait didn’t they already have a fucking huge house?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like picking the penthouse was the right choice after all, Onee-sama.{Looks like picking the penthouse room was right, Onee-sama.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’d better hurr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, Ginko. You’re going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I requested for father to build the apartments here so you would be closer to your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will not be allowed to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even bette{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, it’ll be much easier to find great sales from here!{And then we can go get our prize, the great deals!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.31,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,All we need are some pencils…{and now this line doesn’t really make sense. Oh well.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing makes me happier than free things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.66,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Weren’t they already cheap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,“Economizing”. Oh, it sounds so marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.62,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I can’t handle much more of this.{Ginko is expressing her disapproval of her sister’s antics}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I’ll be going ahead by ca{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll be home{\fsp-0.5} {\fsp}late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:08.53,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama is busy toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don’t hurr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, we’re going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it’s Ginko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you guys moved into the new apartment complex!{マンション (n) large apartment (from mansion); apartment house; FUCK YOU JAPAN}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, your old house was amazing too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father is the owner of these apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that, we can live on whatever floor we want, but the penthouse is definitely the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I’ll invite you over someda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, your scarf is a little crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, we really need to…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We’re going to be late, so let’s chat late{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.63,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,What the heck is it with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:26.47,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Ah, I barely made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.93,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the two of\Nthem are always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.81,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That’s just not the way things are between my sister and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.95,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Holding hands like that… how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H2E1D1E&}Class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Class representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong? Come by the office later to pick up the printouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re also a class representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone pushed the job on you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}had{\i0} to run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I become a fifth grade{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, I’m going to run for the student council, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H2E1D1E&}Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll definitely be elected president!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu-chan, can you please help me with the next part on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, Ginko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s this part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This part here helps to explain this other part here, which leads to—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu-chan, you’re amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me help you carry that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She’s just letting herself get used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don’t seem bus{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help pass these out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, but we’re a little busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Echigoya-san is really annoying, don’t you think?{asdfj -> Echigoya}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:06:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-chan, sorry about what happened earlie{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn’t I tell you to not follow me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We walk home the same wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu-chan, are you heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, we made a little bit too much for toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, so please take this home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, Asu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are today’s leftovers. Take them with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu-chan! I have some leftovers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu-chan, wait! You’d better take this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way you and your sister get by on your own is really something.{You’re working so hard together with your siste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, that’s amazing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s rare to see that these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, this is from our store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. Extras, extras, take ’em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you’ve grown a bit talle{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.37,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,What do you mean it’s “really something”?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.78,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’m also—I’m also trying my best with my older siste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.{and an absurdly rich father who buys everything for them…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.98,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Why is it? Why is it—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won’t lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.16,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I won’t lose to you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.02,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Wh{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, wh{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:29.28,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Just because she’s nice{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, has more\Nfriends, and gets along with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:33.31,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama and I are just so much, much, much—!{better implied by zutto?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had that long-range telescope that you asked for yesterday carried up from the ground floo{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You asked for it so suddenl{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, I was wondering how on earth you were planning to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You plan on doing some pretty risky things with it, right?{BORDERLINE ILLEGAL}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re going to use this to…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scout out all the supermarkets in the city for super-extraordinary sales, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s wonderful, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it’s for the great cause of economization, I’ll even lend you a helicopter if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, I don’t think we need to go that far…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever you’re doing, it’s a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should search every single supermarket for deals, even if it takes you the whole da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.{Even if you have to spend the whole da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, you have to find out every supermarket that has special sales.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.67,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’m sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:30.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That’s not why I asked for the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go now, so I’ll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You’re busy today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we have the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I won’t be back until late tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Have a good da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistress, I’ve finished adjusting the settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begone.{you may go}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.95,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’m aware that I really shouldn’t be doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:10.50,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,but I have to do it so I can find out just what it is that’s so different about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.41,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,We should be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.63,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Even so, even so…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.45,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Yamada Asu!{YAMADA ASS}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.51,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I will definitely not lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Comment: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:14.23,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I remember the part when she got a telescope. I don’t remember the part when she bugged their house with cameras and microphones. Or maybe the telescope has SUPER ULTRA XRAY MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.63,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,It’s delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:14.23,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,The eggs and spinach is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:19.39,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Two days ago, I found the spinach on sale for 40 yen per bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.16,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I cooked it with some eggs I found yesterday for 58 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! The spinach from the sale that I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:38.81,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Why does she open her\Nmouth so wide while eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.74,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama would never do such an improper thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:46.22,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,She even has grains of rice stuck to her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.50,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Why do they act so uncivilized?
Comment: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs80\pos(205.78,303)}( ﾟДﾟ)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, your face has some rice stuck to it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh m{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, you’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:02.61,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Ah, Onee-chan, the miso soup also came out really well toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ve never laughed during a meal before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talking with a full mouth is simply reprehensible behavior!{lol leaving it like this unless someone tells me to tone it down}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:42.05,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Today’s a holida{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, so she’s sleeping on the floor in the middle of the day?{休み [やすみ] 1: rest; recess; respite; 2: vacation; holiday; absence; suspension;}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.32,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’ve never seen Onee-sama being that laz{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.06,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Even until she goes to bed, she’s always energetic and—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.27,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, perhaps you’re a little too energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:05.50,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Why does she always seem so happy to take care of her troublesome older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,It’s rough, isn’t it, Yamada Asu.{flat what}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:17.97,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,My sister is never troublesome or dependent on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kyou-chan, Asu-chan, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s this, the two of you are out for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two sure seem to get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re nothing like my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They’re always fighting with each othe{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:39.42,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,They could learn a thing or two from you guys.{wait, so she has the microphones on asu and kyou? and what’s their workable range?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.76,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,No wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, you’re flattering us, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Comment: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,WEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEH?!?!?!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, go ahead and pick whichever one you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll take this one—the dried tuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll go with the picked plum, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.59,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Let’s eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, this pickled plum rice ball is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All they ever think about is food, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All rice balls taste the same no matter who makes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There’s absolutely no reason for me to be jealous of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:15.79,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Asu-chan, you’re early toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for yesterda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have the day off toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, so I came together with my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.62,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Miste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, do you have anything that’s especially cheap today?{Miste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, are there any cheap fish?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:28.22,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Those two have been together since they woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistress Ginko, don’t you think that spying on people is a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m through with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watching any more would be a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason I’ve been on edge toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It kind of feels like someone is watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s kinda odd, Asu.{silly?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, isn’t it time for you to deliver the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is bad! Today’s the evening edition, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, can you take these home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They’re a little heav{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dinner is read{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(492,1994,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistress Ginko, we’ve completed the dinner preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.{LULZ, "very well"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, is there something you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father hasn’t come home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father has not yet returned from his trip to Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And your mother—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s enough. You’re dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu! This Salmon Meunière is the best!{I shit you not they’re eating french food (capitalized and accented for full irony). ムニエル (n) meuniere (fre:) -> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meuniere_sauce}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man from the fish market was nice enough to sell us this salmon at a really low price,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the side dishes are from the owner of the vegetable stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,“Meunier” certainly has a rich sound to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I only sprinkled a few croûtons on top.{more accents for frenchie lulz}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.41,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’m all right.{HOT GINKO BATHTUB SCENE UNF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.29,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’m fine with being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.40,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I {\i0}was{\i1} fine, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.93,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,But still, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Why am I still drawn to the light from that window?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come over to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wha—?{I am Kyou, this is my derpface: "HURR DURR DERP A HERPDERP"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you before that I’d invite you over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it’s already so late, and shouldn’t you ask your family for permission firs—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There’s nobody there to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! It’s so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, isn’t it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The building over there, the tallest one, is ours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with that one, and that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this area we own a bunch—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, Onee-chan! We’re in someone else’s house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can’t fall asleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, it’s just that she’s usually asleep by this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-cha—!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, she really fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She’s not a very reliable older siste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s why you’re always working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s tough, isn’t it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s not tough at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}. Don’t lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it’s for Onee-chan, I’ll do my very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, she attends school and works as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She’s really the one who has it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because{\fsp-0.5} {\fsp}I{\fsp-0.5} {\fsp}can’t get a real job yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for Onee-chan’s sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to make our home the one place in the world where she doesn’t have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where she doesn’t have to work hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, this fried sweet potato is also really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, we’ll head home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, it’s time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes… It’s delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez…{JESUS H CHRIST}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.03,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,What can I do for my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:56.46,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama always does her best to meet the expectations of those around he{\fsp-1}r{\fsp},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:59.40,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1560)}and I’ve never heard her once complain about how tough it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:04.40,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama is the one who is always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:11.67,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,No, I was the one who abandoned he{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistress Kinko, will it be satisfactory to leave Mistress Ginko’s new clothes here?{argh verb tenses and general phraseology}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure{\fsp-0.5}. {\fsp}Just leave them on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s fine. I’ll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I’ll retire for toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re not asleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should hurry to bed, Ginko. You have school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Onee-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still some things that I have to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My laundry—you’re the one who always folds it for me, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, please don’t push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko.{GODDAMN FUCKING LASER EYES}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.82,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Dear Onee-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:52.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,{\t(1596,3514,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&)}today I noticed something for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.24,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I was the one who was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:58.33,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I was always thinking only about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:04.15,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I didn’t even notice how much you have been taking care of me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.25,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:11.25,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,The most precious feelings are those that two people share for each othe{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:14.62,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That’s why I love you, Onee-sama.{THIS IS MY THESIS, MY MASTERWORK}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be able to create it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where she doesn’t have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please accept this chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan has someone who she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor Sisters’ Story:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,“A day of Jealous{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, Chocolates, and Valentines”.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please watch it!
